  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Corona is rearing its head again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dr. Samitha Ginige, Head of the Epidemiology Department, said that there is a risk of the spread of the corona virus again in Sri Lanka and yesterday (18th) 62 people infected with the corona virus were identified.",
        "The specialist doctor said this in a press conference held today (19th) in Colombo regarding the increase in corona infected people."
      ],
